            .typography
              p That we have big plans for the future and soon we will issue our token, which will be traded on all major crypto-currency exchanges of the world!
        +e.block
          +e.H4.title How much commission will I receive as part of the referral programme?
            span 
          +e.content
            .typography
              p That we have big plans for the future and soon we will issue our token, which will be traded on all major crypto-currency exchanges of the world!

        +e.block
          +e.H4.title Can I deposit funds and trade before my account is verified?
            span 
          +e.content
            .typography
              p That we have big plans for the future and soon we will issue our token, which will be traded on all major crypto-currency exchanges of the world!
        
        +e.block
          +e.H4.title How can I change the address I entered during registration?
            span 
          +e.content
            .typography
              p That we have big plans for the future and soon we will issue our token, which will be traded on all major crypto-currency exchanges of the world!
        
        +e.block
          +e.H4.title Is 2FA mandatory?
            span 
          +e.content
            .typography
              p That we have big plans for the future and soon we will issue our token, which will be traded on all major crypto-currency exchanges of the world!
         
        +e.block
          +e.H4.title How do you deal with corporate actions?
            span 
          +e.content
            .typography
              p That we have big plans for the future and soon we will issue our token, which will be traded on all major crypto-currency exchanges of the world!
  // 
  +b.SECTION.create.section
    .container
      +e.buttons
        +b.A(href="signup.html", class="btn --gr-blue --large") 
          span TO CREATE A WEB WALLET NOW
  //
  include partials/_social
  //
  +footer()

